    <date day="23" month="January" year="2013"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo reiterates the assignment of an IPv4 address block (192.0.0.0/24) to IANA.  It also instructs IANA to restructure its IPv4 and IPv6 Special-Purpose Address Registries.  Upon restructuring, the aforementioned registries will record all special-purpose address blocks, maintaining a common set of information regarding each address block.
	 </t>
